                <head>145. Summary of Conclusions of Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d145fn1">Source: <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1"
                            >Carter</persName> Library, National Security Affairs, Staff Material,
                        Office File, Box 8, Meeting File, <gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss>
                        Meeting: #67, Held 3/24/78. Secret. The meeting was held in the White House
                        Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
